{"tid":1165834,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"如果香港變內地城市, 樓價點睇?","createTime":"2019-05-22T05:07:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T04:38:23.000Z","uid":127807,"like":33,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"30190b330344c2ac6990ffcd8d0e6695013f67f8","tid":1165834,"uid":127807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:07:17.000Z","msg":"巴絲們睇升定跌?<br />\n升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1005674-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E5%BD%AD%E5%AE%9A%E5%BA%B7%EF%BC%9A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9B%9E%E6%AD%B8%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F%E3%80%8C%E6%9C%80%E5%A3%9E%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8B%E3%80%8D+\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1005674-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%25BD%25AD%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%25BA%25B7%25EF%25BC%259A%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25AD%25B8%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E4%25BE%2586%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%2594%259F%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A3%259E%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25BA%258B%25E3%2580%258D%2B&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6Tfno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=d0bfc298\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1005674-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%25BD%25AD%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%25BA%25B7%25EF%25BC%259A%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25AD%25B8%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E4%25BE%2586%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%2594%259F%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A3%259E%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25BA%258B%25E3%2580%258D%2B&h=4f6ae521\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1005674-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E5%BD%AD%E5%AE%9A%E5%BA%B7%EF%BC%9A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9B%9E%E6%AD%B8%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F%E3%80%8C%E6%9C%80%E5%A3%9E%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8B%E3%80%8D+</a><br />\n<br />\n    星島日報 <br />\n    更新時間 2019年5月22日12:07<br />\n<br />\n前港督彭定康在倫敦出席一個論壇前，再次評論特區政府推動逃犯條例修訂。他形容，港政修訂逃犯條例是香港回歸以來發生「最壞的事」，有關條例有如移除香港及內地的「防火牆」，香港市民要承受面對內地司法制度的風險。<br />\n<br />\n彭定康說，外界對修例發出很多警告，他並不感到意外，認為修例會拆走香港及內地的防火牆，同時破壞中國對「一國兩制」的承諾，亦有機會危害香港作為一個國際貿易中心。<br />\n<br />\n他又擔心，若內地開始視香港作為如深圳或上海一般的內地地市，國際社會會認為香港不再是特別行政區。<br />\n<br />\n彭又說，自國家主席習近平在2012年掌權以來，香港的自由社會及法治不斷惡化，情況與習近平在內地收緊管治一脈相承，他說，正當外界討論中國在21世紀的角色時，中國仍未證明是可以信任。<br />\n<br />\n他警告，若果中國開始將香港當成好像深圳或上海一樣的內地城市，國際社會很快就會開始認為，香港不再是特區。"},{"pid":"7ff6fb4b167de928e60c80e696068457d77f9740","tid":1165834,"uid":97426,"like":10,"dislike":12,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:19:12.000Z","msg":"成班廢淡望跌市咪又係買唔到樓又想上車<br />\n講到變成內地城市你咪又係想買樓住喺度<br />\n定還是你係專才全世界都爭住要你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係移民快啲走啦冇人留你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e4c5c02d22b834503cdaad906deb44303f9bc9","tid":1165834,"uid":5267,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:21:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e3c63e985a29e8e5fcc0eadbeb8be2fd81d2981","tid":1165834,"uid":127807,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:21:57.000Z","msg":"我睇其實都係會升"},{"pid":"27e6f92b1dac2bcb3c6c649848c1d119400684cc","tid":1165834,"uid":97426,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:33:01.000Z","msg":"好簡單  大陸人落嚟香港只會越來越多<br />\n我本身都係淡友   但睇政府d政策<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1458636-20190521.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1458636-20190521.htm&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6Tfno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=3b3669f1\" data